ma)|''Napakymppi'']]\n| [[:fi:Markus Similia|Markus Similia]] (1985)<br>[[:fi:Kari Salmelainen|Kari Salmelainen]] (1985\u20132002)<br>Joanna Kantola (2001\u20132002)<br>[[Janne Kataja]] (2017\u20132019)\n| [[MTV]] (1985\u20131992)<br>[[MTV3]] (1993\u20132002)<br>[[Nelonen]] (2017\u20132019)\n| 1985\u20132002<br>2017\u20132019\n|-\n| style=\"background:#FFC0CB;\" rowspan=2 |{{flag|France}}\n|rowspan=2 |[[:fr:Tournez man\u00e8ge !|''Tournez Man\u00e8ge !'']]\n| [[:fr:\u00c9velyne Leclercq|\u00c9velyne Leclercq]]<br>[[:fr:Simone Garnier|Simone Garnier]]<br>[[:fr:Fabienne \u00c9gal|Fabienne \u00c9gal]]\n|rowspan=2 |[[TF1]]\n| 1985\u20131993\n|-\n| [[:fr:S\u00e9bastien Cauet|S\u00e9bastien Cauet]]\n| 2009\u20132010\n|-\n|style=\"background:#FFC0CB;\" rowspan=3 |{{flag|Germany}}\n| ''[[:de:Herzblatt (Fernsehsendung)|Herzblatt]]''\n| [[Rudi Carrell]] (1987\u20131993)<br>[[Rainhard Fendrich]] (1993\u20131997)<br>Hera Lind (1997\u20131998)<br>Christian Clerici (1998\u20131999)<br>Pierre Geisensetter (1999\u20132001)<br>[[J\u00f6rg Pilawa]] (2001\u20132004)<br>Alexander Mazza (2005)\n| [[Das Erste]]\n| 1987\u20132005\n|-\n| ''[[:de:Herz ist Trumpf (Fernsehshow)|Herz ist Trumpf]]''\n| [[:de:Stephan Lehmann (Moderator)|Stephan Lehmann]]\n| [[Sat.1]]\n| 1992\u20131993\n|-\n| ''Herz sucht Liebe''\n| [[Thomas Ohrner]]\n| [[Sat.1 Gold]]\n| 2016\n|-\n| style=\"background:#FFC0CB;\" |{{flag|Hungary}}\n| ?\n| ?\n| [[RTL Klub]]\n| ?\n|-\n| style=\"background:#FFC0CB;\" |{{flag|Ireland}}\n| ''Blind Date''\n| [[Al Porter]]\n| [[TV3 Ireland|TV3]]\n| 2017\n|-\n| style=\"background:#FFC0CB;\" |{{flag|Israel}}\n| ?\n| ?\n| [[Channel 2 (Israel)|Channel 2]] ([[Keshet (TV)|Keshet]])\n| ?\n|-\n| style=\"background:#FFC0CB;\" |{{flag|Italy}}\n| ''[[:it:Il gioco delle coppie|Il gioco delle coppie]]''<br>''Il nuovo gioco delle coppie''\n| [[:it:Marco Predolin|Marco Predolin]] (1985\u20131990)<br>[[:it:Corrado Tedeschi|Corrado Tedeschi]] (1990\u20131992)<br>[[:it:Giorgio Mastrota|Giorgio Mastrota]] 